cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper involves computer vision (CV) techniques for road detection using LIDAR and camera data, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the cs.CV sub-category. Additionally, the use of deep learning methods such as fully convolutional neural networks (FCNs) and the fusion of multimodal data also suggest that it could belong to the cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE sub-categories. Finally, the application of these techniques to robotics and autonomous vehicles suggests that it could also belong to the cs.RO sub-category.
